%^BOLD%^-=%^RESET%^%^RED%^War Domain%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

A more varied domain than one might expect, the 
war domain grants the priest with a wide range 
of abilities all centered upon battle.  Some 
are designed to aid his battle prowess while 
the third is meant to help him seek out a
particular foe.

The war domain contains the following spells:
Seeking Sword (3rd), Offensive Summoning (5th), Berserker (7th)

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: Nilith

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
     